OL,4,Claunches would boost jobs and
OL,5,Cinvestment ` MP
OL,7,FBritain's space industry would receive
OL,8,Fa jobs and investment boost if a cap
OL,9,Fon liabilities for companies launching
OL,10,Fspacecraft is approved by Parliament,
OL,11,Faccording to an MP.
OL,13,FLabour's John Grady said current
OL,14,Flegislation is acting as a "deterrent"
OL,15,Fto investors, and a legal cap would
OL,16,Fprotect companies from costs if an
OL,17,Faccident or damage to property
OL,18,Foccurred.
