OL,7,FThe MP for Glasgow East's Space
OL,8,FIndustry (Indemnities) Bill, which
OL,9,Fseeks to put a liability cap on a
OL,10,F"firm footing" by amending 2018
OL,11,Flegislation, is scheduled to be
OL,12,Fconsidered at second reading on Friday.
OL,14,FFormer lawyer Mr Grady told the PA
OL,15,Fnews agency: "Investors like to know
OL,16,Fhow much they're in for, unlimited
OL,17,Fliabilities are a concern."
