OL,7,FHe added: "If you look at the journey
OL,8,Fof the space industry over the last
OL,9,Ffew years, at one point we couldn't
OL,10,Flaunch our own stuff, but now for
OL,11,Finstance we've got a spaceport up
OL,12,Fnorth in Scotland, in Shetland, which
OL,13,Fwill hopefully have its first launch
OL,14,Fsoon, and of course we've had launches
OL,15,Fin Cornwall as well."
