OL,5,Cinvestment ` MP
OL,7,FThe MP continued: "There's a huge
OL,8,Fnumber of jobs, trades that can be
OL,9,Fgenerated by the space industry. So it
OL,10,Fcan create employment. It's also
OL,11,Fimportant in terms of just being able
OL,12,Fto have our own industrial clusters."
OL,14,FMr Grady described the space industry
OL,15,Fas an "industry of the future", before
OL,16,Fgoing on to say: "At the minute,
OL,17,Falthough Government policy is that we
OL,18,Fcap the liability for people who
OL,19,Foperate and send spacecrafts up, it's
OL,20,Fnot got 100% firm footing.
