OL,7,F"And the issue with that is it's a
OL,8,Fdeterrent for people to invest in
OL,9,Fspace, and the space industry in the
OL,10,FUnited Kingdom.
OL,12,F"So it's been a fairly longstanding
OL,13,Fdiscussion over the last few years for
OL,14,Fthe need to make sure that the Act on
OL,15,Fthe face of it has the ability to cap
OL,16,Fliability for space operators."
OL,18,FThe liability cap will be specified in
OL,19,Flicences, which are granted to the
OL,20,Fspace operator by the Civil Aviation
OL,21,FAuthority (CAA).
